documents.title: Getting Started with Papier
documents.content:
Welcome to Papier, your simple document management app. This is your first document, feel free to edit or delete it.

You can create new documents by clicking the 'New Document' button in the documents list page.

Happy writing!

documents.title: Project Ideas
documents.content:
## App Features

- Document organization with folders
- Rich text editor
- Dark/light theme toggle
- Document sharing
- Export to PDF

## Tech Stack

- React with TypeScript
- TanStack Query for data fetching
- Shadcn UI components
- Vite for development
- Lorem Ipson
